Title: Congratulating Muriel Neufeld posthumously for being inducted into the 26th Annual May W. Newburger Women's Roll of Honor by the Town of North Hempstead
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION congratulating Muriel Neufeld posthumously upon the occasion of being inducted into the 26th Annual May W. Newburger Women's Roll of Honor by the Town of North Hempstead, in conjunction with the observance of Women's History Month
